data.description: ****** OFFER DEADLINE SET FOR 12/26/2023****  Welcome to 1913 Rose Place in the sought-after community of Upper Marlboro, Maryland. This charming 3 / 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of classic charm and modern conveniences, perfect for those seeking a peaceful and comfortable living experience. The property has been recently updated and is very well maintained.  As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting foyer with Italian marble floors and custom paint work, with warm, natural lights. The living room is spacious and inviting, featuring a cozy fireplace, large windows, and plenty of natural light. The formal dining room is perfect for hosting dinner parties and family gatherings, while the well-appointed kitchen features sleek modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a center island, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. Sit at the Breakfast nook and enjoy a serene view of the backyard! The cozy fireplaces (2 ) serve as the perfect centerpiece for those chilly nights. The updated kitchen boasts sleek stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an abundance of cabinetry for all your storage needs. The formal dining room provides a sophisticated space for dinner parties and holidays. On the main level, you will find a huge Home Office, and off the kitchen is the large converted bedroom or den, depending on your desired use of this space.  The primary bedroom suite is a true oasis, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a spa-like bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower. Two additional bedrooms are located down the hall and share a full bathroom.  This gated property offers a  backyard that is perfect for outdoor entertaining, with a spacious patio, basketball court,  plenty of grassy areas for kids and pets to play, and plenty of privacy. The detached garage provides secure parking for one car, and there is ample driveway and street parking for additional vehicles.  Conveniently located just minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment, 1913 Rose Place is the ideal place to call home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful property. Schedule a showing today!  The Septic was pumped in February 2019 and inspected again in 2020 at the time of purchase; the roof is approximately 18 years old and roof warrantied by the Solar company due to the installed Solar  Panels, which also saves you money and possibly credit from Pepco.    ***Offers will be reviewed and presented as they come in***
